Dijkstra (uniform-cost search)

state space (mnozina vsetkych stavov/vrcholov)
initial state (pociatocny stav)
action: actions(state)   (hrana alebo pseudo tah v 15puzzle)
transition model: result(state, action)  ()
goal test: isGoal(state)    (true alebo false, ci stav je cielovy)
(step) path cost: cost(state, action)     (dlzka hrany)

explored (prejdene)
frontiers (nasledne preskumane v dalsom kroku)
unexplored set (nepreskumane)

node = state + pointer to parent node + parent action

BFS - fronta = najkratsia cesta v neohodnotenych grafoch
Dijkstra - prioritna fronta = najkratsia cesta v ohodnotenom grafe
pouzijeme haldu (priority queue)




